{"tid":1378893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［7•28］政府回應港島區示威活動","createTime":"2019-07-28T16:58:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T17:02:44.000Z","uid":243761,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"08700dea612a557824a8b33794f2652829b0c482","tid":1378893,"uid":243761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:58:43.000Z","msg":"政府回應港島區示威活動<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n　　就昨日（七月二十八日）在港島區的示威活動，政府發言人作以下回應：<br />\n<br />\n　　昨天自下午開始有市民在港島不同地區進行未經批准的集結，其中在上環及西環一帶有激進示威者作出暴力行為，包括向警務人員擲磚、縱火，甚至以載有燃燒中紙皮的手推車推向警方防線，對警務人員以至其他市民構成危險。激進示威者目無法紀，以暴力破壞社會安寧，我們予以強烈譴責，會繼續全力支持警隊嚴正執法，遏止所有暴力行為，盡快回復社會秩序。<br />\n<br />\n　　此外，在銅鑼灣有市民佔據馬路，更有人破壞公物，設置路障阻塞交通，嚴重影響巴士及電車等公共服務。該等行為不但違法，亦對其他市民造成不便，我們對此表示遺憾，並再次呼籲市民表達意見時應和平理性，不應以身試法。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年7月29日（星期一）<br />\n香港時間0時17分<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n講嚟講去都係個兩篤屁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c6aaf83b21799702bd5cec8500fec87ab84bcc0","tid":1378893,"uid":243761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:58:55.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"eaaa4431395bdf16ccff451f2aaa841ad11ab5b6","tid":1378893,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:59:00.000Z","msg":"我會罷工"},{"pid":"28dba786628d1a0a5df150a2567b2e27c859c37d","tid":1378893,"uid":243761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:59:05.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"60f42d8dbfab912479b1f2bb27361592ee1de060","tid":1378893,"uid":243761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:59:15.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"449a567c1981b921d37aeff60295122dc5f9515f","tid":1378893,"uid":170297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:59:37.000Z","msg":"網誌治港"},{"pid":"6fd69112d2926d3448e0ddaca334a8ac360bf3b1","tid":1378893,"uid":19299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:00:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />強烈譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c41d5c27d911f66f4cc035af4d336ea7fe4baf2e","tid":1378893,"uid":12412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:01:37.000Z","msg":"得喇得喇"},{"pid":"f976027a706dd6df9c208497582c2b8df8db319b","tid":1378893,"uid":65790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:02:42.000Z","msg":"on9,政府真係易做<br />\n咁多人表達意見但回覆永遠都係呢篇垃圾"},{"pid":"93ba8a59504ffdbc10b64f5a074daff021db0752","tid":1378893,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:02:44.000Z","msg":"一篇文<br />\n改個日期"}]}